<p>专门人才：professional personnel</p>
<p>创新：innovation</p>
<p><strong>经典模板句练习：</strong></p>
<p>1. 通过阅读，人们能更好的学会感恩、有责任心和与人合作。(CET-4)。</p>
<p>By/Through reading, people can better learn to be grateful, responsible and cooperative.</p>
<p>2. 美国网民更多的是受实际需要的驱使，用互联网为工具发电子邮件、买卖商品、做研究、规划旅程或付款。(CET-4)。</p>
<p>The American netizens are more likely to be driven by practical needs, using the Internet as a tool to send emails, buy and sell products, make researches, arrange trips or make payments.</p>
<p>3. 中国的创新正以前所未有的速度蓬勃发展。(CET-4)。</p>
<p>China’s innovation is developing/flourishing at an unprecedented speed.</p>
<p>4. 中国父母往往过于关注孩子的学习。(CET-4)。</p>
<p>Chinese parents usually pay too much attention to their children’ s study / the study of their children.</p>
